full_text:
I read the instructions for this thing, and it seems its only a visual indication (via bar-graph LEDs) of the average audio output level from a recorder that has direct monitoring of recorded sounds (like 3 head recorder) coming out of the headphone socket. They say the gizmo only works with recorders that have direct monitoring during record mode. Sooo its a visual guide to what the recorder is hearing during a record sesson. Seems not much benefit for $145.
JEFF


